canonical:
  title: 和藍山驛樓留題
  author: 林惟正
  language: lzh
  text: 古驛登臨足勝遊舜欽 林泉乘興訪淸幽韓維 萬家煙樹千重綠齊己 千簇雲山萬壑流周貫 午夜溪聲來枕上揚蟠 百年心事到心頭樂天 曉來爲報樓西月錢起 且爲詩人更小留李紳
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 和藍山驛樓留題
  author: 林惟正
  language: lzh
  text: 古驛登臨足勝遊。舜欽。 林泉乘興訪淸幽。韓維。 萬家煙樹千重綠。齊己。 千簇雲山萬壑流。周貫。 午夜溪聲來枕上。揚蟠。 百年心事到心頭。樂天。 曉來爲報樓西月。錢起。 且爲詩人更小留。李紳。
korean:
  title: 남산역루에서 유제에 화답하며
  author: 임유정
  language: kor
  text: |-
    낡은 역에 올라오니 흐뭇한 멋진 놀이 순흠(舜欽)
    임천에 흥을 타서 그윽한 곳 찾아왔네 한유(韓維)
    집집의 연기낀 나무는 천 겹으로 푸르구나 제기(齊己)
    올망졸망 구름 낀 산엔 골짜기마다 흐르는 물 주관(周貫)
    한밤중 시냇물소리가 베개맡에 들려 오니 양반(揚蟠)
    한평생 지낸 심사가 마음에 떠오르는구나 낙천(樂天)
    새벽녘 누각 서쪽 달에게 이르노니 전기(錢起)
    잠깐 더 시인을 위해 머무른들 어떠리 이신(李紳)
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0160_010_0570&viewSync=OT
english:
  title: A Poem Left at Lanshan Relay Station Tower, in Response to Others
  author: Lim Yu-jeong
  language: eng
  text: |-
    Climbing the ancient relay station, what splendid pleasure greets the eye.
    Following my heart through groves and waters, I seek the quiet, hidden place.
    From every house the smoke-wreathed trees stretch forth in thousand-layered green.
    Through misty mountains and clouded peaks, a thousand valleys flow with streams.
    At the depth of night, the sound of the creek reaches my pillow,
    And all the cares of my hundred years rise up to fill my heart.
    At dawn I speak to the moon hanging west of this tower:
    Why not linger a moment longer for the sake of poetry?
  footnotes:
    - This is a collaborative poem (唱和詩), where each line was written by a different poet in response to previous verses. The names in parentheses indicate the original authors of each couplet being echoed.
    - Lanshan (藍山) Relay Station was a famous historical waystation where poets would gather and leave commemorative verses.
